<body><div class=WordSection1>
<div class="brand">📚 ENGLISH CODING · 영어코딩</div>
<h1>🤖 AI001 Week 1 — English Worksheet</h1>
<p><strong>Topic:</strong> First Prompt — Meeting Replit Agent · <strong>Course:</strong> AI Coding with Replit Agent · <strong>Time:</strong> about 45 minutes</p>
<p>This week you meet your AI builder, <strong>Replit Agent</strong>. You do not type code. You type a <strong>prompt</strong> — an instruction in plain words — and the AI builds a web page for you.</p>
<hr />
<h2>1 · Predict 🔮</h2>
<p>Read each prompt. Before you imagine the AI building it, write what you think will appear on the screen.</p>
<pre><code>Build a simple web page that shows &quot;Hello World&quot;.
</code></pre>
<p><strong>What will be on the page? Just words, or pictures too?</strong></p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<pre><code>Build a web page. The title says &quot;Hello World&quot;,
the background is light yellow, and the text is dark green.
</code></pre>
<p><strong>How is this result different from the first one? What changed?</strong></p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<pre><code>Make a page.
</code></pre>
<p><strong>This prompt is very short. What might go wrong? Will you get exactly what you pictured?</strong></p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<hr />
<h2>2 · Spot the Weak Prompt 🐛</h2>
<p>Each prompt below was meant to get a clear result, but it is too vague or missing something. Read what the student <strong>wanted</strong>, then rewrite the prompt so the AI knows exactly what to build. After that, explain why the first one was weak.</p>
<p><strong>Prompt A</strong> — The student wanted a page that says their name, <strong>Minji</strong>, in big letters.</p>
<pre><code>Make my name.
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Hint:</strong> the AI does not know your name, the size, or that you want a web page.</p>
<p><strong>Write a clearer prompt:</strong></p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>Why was the first one weak? Why does yours work better?</strong></p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>Prompt B</strong> — The student wanted a page with a <strong>blue background</strong> and <strong>white text</strong> that says "Welcome".</p>
<pre><code>Make it blue.
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Hint:</strong> make <em>what</em> blue? And what should the page say?</p>
<p><strong>Write a clearer prompt:</strong></p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>Why was the first one weak? Why does yours work better?</strong></p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>Prompt C</strong> — The student already has a "Hello World" page and now wants the <strong>text bigger</strong> and the <strong>background pink</strong>.</p>
<pre><code>Change everything.
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Hint:</strong> name the two things you want changed.</p>
<p><strong>Write a clearer prompt:</strong></p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>Why was the first one weak? Why does yours work better?</strong></p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<hr />
<h2>3 · Try It and Show Me 📸</h2>
<p>Open Replit and turn on the Agent. Build a web page with <strong>your own name</strong> on it, using only prompts. Try changing the background color and making the text bigger by writing a second prompt.</p>
<p>When you finish, come back here. Send a <strong>photo or video</strong> of your page, then explain what you did. Use these sentence starters — write 4 to 6 sentences total.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>My first prompt asked the AI to …</p>
<p>When I read the result, I saw …</p>
<p>My second prompt changed …</p>
<p>One word I added to make it clearer was …</p>
<p>Something surprised me when …</p>
<p>If I had more time, I would …</p>
</blockquote>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<hr />
<h2>4 · Save Your Prompts 🗒️</h2>
<p>Write down the <strong>exact prompts</strong> you used today, word for word. You will reuse and improve them in later weeks, so keep them.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Prompt 1:</p>
<p>Prompt 2:</p>
<p>Prompt 3 (if you wrote one):</p>
</blockquote>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<hr />
<h3>Submit ✅</h3>
<p>Send this worksheet + a photo (or video) of your page + your prompt list to teacher on KakaoTalk.</p>
<div class="footer">영어코딩 · <b>english-coding.co.uk</b></div>
</div></body></html>
